@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = 

### ========================================
### AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ========================================

### Registrar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Teste de Registro",
    "email": "teste@example.com",
    "password": "senha123"
}

### 
# Após registrar, copie o token da resposta e cole na variável @token acima
# Ou use o login abaixo para obter um novo token

### Fazer login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "teste@example.com",
    "password": "senha123"
}

### 
# Copie o token da resposta e cole na variável @token no topo do arquivo
# Exemplo: @token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### ========================================
### WORKOUTS - CRUD Completo
### ========================================

### Listar todos os treinos
GET {{baseUrl}}/workouts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Criar novo treino
POST {{baseUrl}}/workouts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Treino A - Peito e Tríceps"
}

###

### Criar outro treino
POST {{baseUrl}}/workouts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Treino B - Costas e Bíceps"
}

###

### Buscar treino por ID (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Atualizar treino (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{id}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Treino A - Atualizado"
}

###

### Deletar treino (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Teste: Criar treino sem nome (erro 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workouts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": ""
}

###

### Teste: Buscar treino inexistente (erro 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workouts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ========================================
### EXERCISES - CRUD Completo
### ========================================

### Listar todos os exercícios
GET {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Criar novo exercício
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Supino Reto",
    "muscle_group": "Peito"
}

###

### Criar outro exercício
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Leg Press",
    "muscle_group": "Perna"
}

###

### Criar exercício sem muscle_group (opcional)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Abdominal"
}

###

### Buscar exercício por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/exercises/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Atualizar exercício
PUT {{baseUrl}}/exercises/{id}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Supino Inclinado",
    "muscle_group": "Peito"
}

###

### Deletar exercício
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/exercises/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Teste: Criar exercício duplicado (erro 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Supino Reto"
}

###

### ========================================
### WORKOUT EXERCISES - Relacionamento
### ========================================

### Listar exercícios de um treino (substitua {workoutId})
GET {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Adicionar exercício ao treino (substitua {workoutId} e {exerciseId})
POST {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "exercise_id": "{exerciseId}",
    "weight": 60.5,
    "sets": 3,
    "reps": 12
}

###

### Atualizar peso/séries/reps (substitua {workoutId} e {exerciseId})
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises/{exerciseId}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "weight": 65.0,
    "sets": 4,
    "reps": 10
}

###

### Atualizar apenas peso (atualização parcial)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises/{exerciseId}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "weight": 70.0
}

###

### Remover exercício do treino
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises/{exerciseId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Teste: Adicionar exercício duplicado (erro 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "exercise_id": "mesmo-exercise-id-de-cima",
    "weight": 60.5,
    "sets": 3,
    "reps": 12
}

###

### Teste: Peso negativo (erro 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "exercise_id": "outro-exercise-id",
    "weight": -10,
    "sets": 3,
    "reps": 12
}

###